{"tid":600322,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"今日小息果陣, 班上個MK仔捉住我行去女神面前","createTime":"2018-03-21T08:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T04:32:57.000Z","uid":129660,"like":20,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"58a0d1719577a23871a72e85993dcd3f5540ce37","tid":600322,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T08:00:54.000Z","msg":"MK仔:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女神:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放小息, 我準備去廁所爆石<br />\n眼尾稍到個MK仔快步向我行近, 條友係班上算係最撚大聲, 最有自信既雜種狗黎<br />\n佢個腹肌都幾勁, 一野拉住我, 一路大聲叫我女神個名<br />\n<br />\nMK仔: 女神同學, 你覺得呢條友個樣毒唔毒呀?<br />\n我: Hello(細聲)<br />\n<br />\n成班MK軍團一齊大聲笑, 我尷尬到面都紅哂<br />\n女神個樣有D驚訝, 望一望條MK, 又望一望我, 但望我既時間短D, 好快就閃開<br />\n女神: Haha,  唔算好毒姐. 你地唔好玩人啦<br />\n<br />\n我係咪有機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c644076b78bba40b6432eef2cbe74044e1d30213","tid":600322,"uid":29080,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"c586c32b4a304cfe220e3f27a4f23d3e2fedb647","tid":600322,"uid":4349,"like":177,"dislike":4,"score":173,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T08:02:26.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀 去強姦"},{"pid":"710cf85d20e628526012923712d6cd07466a4057","tid":600322,"uid":7915,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T08:02:27.000Z","msg":"真心 上得"},{"pid":"111c3c52a48d5ed75b1d8fc807dbd2eedf537db6","tid":600322,"uid":52068,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T08:03:12.000Z","msg":"憐憫可憐的小動物"},{"pid":"8c77df9bcf0c13b5400836d4c52601f8569747f7","tid":600322,"uid":167389,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T08:03:15.000Z","msg":"咁似靜宜同大雄嘅"},{"pid":"01d19de9e9a88dffee560ba191057d6ec6c57586","tid":600322,"uid":148042,"like":1,